<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      metal:use-macro="base.macros['base']">

<tal:block metal:fill-slot="content" class="main-content">

  <tal:if tal:condition="title | nothing"><h1>${title}</h1></tal:if>

  <tal:if tal:condition="success">
    <div id="request_received_content">

      <p>Your request was received and will be processed soon.</p>

      <h2>What will happen next...</h2>

      <p>Expect to receive an email directing you to set up your remote access.</p>

      <p>To gain remote access, you will need to set up a multi-factor toen. You can do this on your Android or Apple mobile device or tablet.</p>
      <h3>While you are waiting...</h3>
      <p>Please download one of the following applications to your IOS or Android device:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.fedorahosted.freeotp">FreeOTP Authenticator for Android Phones</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/freeotp-authenticator/id872559395">FreeOTP for iPhone</a></li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </tal:if>

  <tal:if tal:condition="not:success">
    <div id="request_received_content">

      <h2>There is an error in the request</h2>

      <p>Please <a href="">re-submit your account request</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </tal:if>


</tal:block>
</html>
